title: CSO Ireland, Number of Private Households by whether or not they have Central Heating by Town, Ireland, 2006
name: CSO Ireland, Number of Private Households by whether or not they have Central Heating by Town, Ireland, 2006
description: This dataset has data on the number of private households by whether or not they have central heating throughout towns in Ireland that have a population of over 1000. The data includes numbers and percentages for the following cases: Yes they have central heating, No they don't have central heating, and they did not state if they have central heating. The towns have been geolocated by their lat/lon position. For more info about the data go to cso.ie/census.
